#: src/CreateMachineDialog.jsx:537
msgid "Bootstrap will enable systemd-networkd and create a shared NAT bridge (vz-cockpit-nspawn, 10.99.0.1/24) on the host. IP forwarding will be enabled. This only runs once — all subsequent NAT containers reuse the same bridge."
